<BaseLayout
  title="Medical Disclaimer"
  description="Medical disclaimer for the RRM Academy website. This site provides educational content about restorative reproductive medicine and does not constitute medical advice."
  canonicalUrl="https://rrmacademy.org/medical-disclaimer"
>
  <div class="page-wrapper prose">
    <div class="container container--narrow">
      <h1>Medical Disclaimer</h1>
      <p class="effective-date">Effective Date: February 22, 2026</p>

      <section class="legal-section">
        <h2>1. Educational Purpose</h2>
        <p>The information provided on this website is for general educational and informational purposes only. The RRM Academy Research Library indexes and summarizes peer-reviewed research to advance professional and public understanding of restorative reproductive medicine.</p>
        <p>Inclusion of any study, article, or publication does not constitute endorsement of its findings, conclusions, or recommendations by the Restorative Reproductive Medicine Foundation Inc.</p>
      </section>

      <section class="legal-section">
        <h2>2. Not Medical Advice</h2>
        <p>This website does not provide medical advice. The content is not intended to be a substitute for professional medical advice, diagnosis, or treatment. <strong>Always seek the advice of your physician or other qualified healthcare provider</strong> with any questions you may have regarding a medical condition.</p>
        <p>Never disregard professional medical advice or delay in seeking it because of something you have read on this site.</p>
      </section>

      <section class="legal-section">
        <h2>3. No Doctor-Patient Relationship</h2>
        <p>Use of this website does not establish a doctor-patient or provider-patient relationship. No information on this site should be construed as the practice of medicine or as personal medical advice directed at any individual visitor.</p>
      </section>

      <section class="legal-section">
        <h2>4. Emergency Notice</h2>
        <p><strong>If you think you may have a medical emergency, call your doctor or 911 immediately.</strong> Do not rely on information found on this website for emergency medical needs.</p>
      </section>

      <section class="legal-section">
        <h2>5. Research Library Disclaimer</h2>
        <p>The RRM Academy Research Library indexes research from a wide range of peer-reviewed journals and academic sources. The views and conclusions expressed in this research are those of the original authors and do not necessarily reflect the views of the Restorative Reproductive Medicine Foundation Inc.</p>
        <p>RRM Academy makes no representations or warranties regarding the accuracy, completeness, or timeliness of the information presented. Scientific understanding evolves, and findings reported in individual studies may be superseded by subsequent research.</p>
      </section>

      <section class="legal-section">
        <h2>6. No Endorsement of Products or Procedures</h2>
        <p>The Foundation does not recommend or endorse any specific tests, physicians, products, procedures, or opinions that may be referenced on this site. Reliance on any information provided through this website is solely at your own risk.</p>
      </section>

      <section class="legal-section">
        <h2>7. Contact</h2>
        <p>If you have questions about this disclaimer, please contact us at:</p>
        <address class="contact-block">
          <strong>Restorative Reproductive Medicine Foundation Inc.</strong><br />
          3401 Hartzdale Dr Ste 103B PMB 3518<br />
          Camp Hill, PA 17011
        </address>
        <p>
          <strong>Contact Form:</strong> <a href="/contact/">rrmacademy.org/contact</a><br />
          <strong>Phone:</strong> (443) 937-3272
        </p>
      </section>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
